description: TrailBOSS Channelizer Drum
short_description:
• Meets MUTCD and NCHRP-350 requirements with or without barricade lights
  • Drum designed to inhibit roll after impact to eliminate further hazards or potential damage
  • Tapered drum design enables nesting for storage or transport
  • Drum handle accommodates one or two Type A or C lights designed to be attached with a standard size bolt and bolt protector
  • Drum Height: 41.27", Drum Diameter (at bottom): 23
  • Choice of 4 different bases: HDPE Drum Snap-On Base, 25 lb. Drum Base, 40 lb. Drum Base and 22.5" Tire Ring
  • 1600 models are constructed of linear low density polyethylene, 1610 models are constructed of high density polyethylene
  • Old TrailBOSS drums and bases are NOT interchangeable with updated TrailBOSS products manufactured after Decembe 2008
  • Plastic Snap-On Base can be weighted down with a sandbag
